http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Shifting-the-factory-showroom/article13978074.ece

The Karnataka Silk Industries Corporation has decided to shift its factory showroom from Manandawadi Road to the spacious Centenary Bhavan located next to the factory. Also, there are plans to tie-up with the Department of Tourism to bring tourists to the factory to promote the Mysore silk saris and help in developing the factory further.As there is ample space at Centenary Bhavan, the showroom will get more space and benefit customers, authorities feel.The KSIC also plans to establish a permanent exhibition on the first floor of the bhavan as part of its proposed all year long sari expo.